1
00:00:27,180 --> 00:00:28,180
I'm Wang Xiaoxiu.

2
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:30,540
I was just an ordinary student.

3
00:00:31,290 --> 00:00:32,930
This girl is Shen Yao.

4
00:00:33,220 --> 00:00:34,210
She's...

5
00:00:35,010 --> 00:00:36,800
She's my girlfriend.

6
00:00:38,050 --> 00:00:39,980
We've been friends since forever.

7
00:00:40,010 --> 00:00:41,800
An embarrassing accident...

8
00:00:42,430 --> 00:00:44,030
brought us closer together.

9
00:00:46,130 --> 00:00:47,090
I thought

10
00:00:47,770 --> 00:00:49,010
it was the start of

11
00:00:49,170 --> 00:00:51,210
our "happily ever after."

12
00:00:52,870 --> 00:00:53,670
However...

13
00:00:57,260 --> 00:00:58,720
the Horadric Cube

14
00:00:58,990 --> 00:01:00,860
disrupted my peaceful life.

15
00:01:05,489 --> 00:01:07,020
Becoming one with the Cube,

16
00:01:07,590 --> 00:01:08,920
I'm stronger than ever.

17
00:01:13,770 --> 00:01:14,550
I realized

18
00:01:15,110 --> 00:01:17,300
I'm now empowered to protect Yao.

19
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:30,630
{\an8}[Caution: Please do not try this at home]

20
00:01:41,660 --> 00:01:43,180
I even left my hometown

21
00:01:43,330 --> 00:01:45,060
to cultivate in the mountains.

22
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:05,290
Although Yao noticed my changes,

23
00:02:05,970 --> 00:02:07,430
I didn't want her to worry.

24
00:02:07,900 --> 00:02:09,160
So I chose to hide it.

25
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:14,160
But I never imagined...

26
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:17,690
that would be our last interaction

27
00:02:17,800 --> 00:02:19,250
before we parted.

28
00:02:22,380 --> 00:02:23,590
Due to my negligence,

29
00:02:24,290 --> 00:02:25,990
Yao was kidnapped by Yan Luo.

30
00:02:28,610 --> 00:02:30,340
He's an irredeemable bastard.

31
00:02:31,020 --> 00:02:33,270
To take revenge on his nemesis Xigu Qin,

32
00:02:33,500 --> 00:02:35,500
he even kidnapped the innocent Yao,

33
00:02:35,590 --> 00:02:37,050
holding her hostage,

34
00:02:37,070 --> 00:02:38,800
in hopes of luring Xigu Qin out.

35
00:02:44,290 --> 00:02:47,489
I'm not interested in the feud between Yan Luo and Xigu Qin.

36
00:02:47,490 --> 00:02:48,510
All I know is

37
00:02:49,110 --> 00:02:51,090
no one is allowed to hurt my Yao.

38
00:02:53,100 --> 00:02:54,970
So I came to this battlefield

39
00:02:55,020 --> 00:02:56,280
with the Cube's powers

40
00:02:56,320 --> 00:02:58,650
to challenge the masters hired by Yan Luo.

41
00:03:00,180 --> 00:03:02,110
No matter how they try to stop me...

42
00:03:05,220 --> 00:03:07,300
no matter how powerful they are...

43
00:03:14,920 --> 00:03:16,520
No matter how many there are,

44
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,440
I will...

45
00:03:22,380 --> 00:03:23,920
I must save my Yao!

46
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:53,720
♪ If I could escape from fate's predetermined path ♪

47
00:03:54,410 --> 00:03:58,680
♪ And touch the true essence of time and space, the ultimate secret ♪

48
00:03:59,050 --> 00:04:03,920
♪ Awakening this extraordinary destiny ♪

49
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:06,590
♪ Awakening another version of myself ♪

50
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:12,550
♪ The clearest, most resilient eyes of yours ♪

51
00:04:12,580 --> 00:04:16,220
♪ Filled with the crystallization of infinite power ♪

52
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:19,370
♪ Releasing my true nature ♪

53
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:22,450
♪ Extracting every breath at lightning speed ♪

54
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:24,570
♪ Shining justice ♪

55
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:29,000
♪ The only truth in the duel ♪

56
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:31,440
♪ Now you guys are hearing my cry ♪

57
00:04:31,700 --> 00:04:33,950
♪ My life was full of regrets ♪

58
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:35,700
♪ Restart ♪

59
00:04:35,750 --> 00:04:37,110
♪ Striving, fighting, honing ♪

60
00:04:37,140 --> 00:04:39,060
♪ Finding the future ♪

61
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:41,380
♪ Do not just dream it, have a try ♪

62
00:04:41,409 --> 00:04:43,950
♪ Nothing can beat me, bravery's in my chest ♪

63
00:04:44,030 --> 00:04:48,530
♪ I'll smash myself to protect your tenderness ♪

64
00:04:48,690 --> 00:04:52,850
♪ Never bow down again ♪

65
00:04:55,030 --> 00:04:58,940
{\an8}[Super Cube]
[Episode 6]

66
00:05:10,950 --> 00:05:13,290
Awesome! You're finally here!

67
00:05:13,530 --> 00:05:14,840
Sure took you long.

68
00:05:20,580 --> 00:05:21,980
An EF wavelength of zero?

69
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,260
Not superhuman?

70
00:05:23,620 --> 00:05:25,020
Not a cultivator either.

71
00:05:25,220 --> 00:05:26,820
Internal power's near zero.

72
00:05:27,650 --> 00:05:29,109
No systematic fighting skills.

73
00:05:29,110 --> 00:05:31,440
Purely fighting with physical strength.

74
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:33,810
Something like...

75
00:05:34,270 --> 00:05:37,560
A body refiner? He'll totally boost my powers!

76
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:41,600
Oops, excuse me.

77
00:05:41,630 --> 00:05:43,819
I got too excited. Where are my manners?

78
00:05:43,820 --> 00:05:45,560
Hello, I'm Kui Jialin.

79
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,130
You can call me Dar-lin.

80
00:05:48,390 --> 00:05:49,390
I'm Wang Xiaoxiu.

81
00:05:50,520 --> 00:05:51,370
How...

82
00:05:52,010 --> 00:05:53,920
are... you?

83
00:05:59,970 --> 00:06:01,260
What a psycho!

84
00:06:01,920 --> 00:06:03,720
Fine! Thank you! And you?

85
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:08,130
His energy sure is clean and pure!

86
00:06:08,700 --> 00:06:10,239
No threat of internal injuries

87
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,770
nor the dullness of mere physical collision.

88
00:06:12,880 --> 00:06:15,140
Purity that melts upon entering my body.

89
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:17,460
His power is like...

90
00:06:18,190 --> 00:06:21,250
like... an unadulterated gem!

91
00:06:21,830 --> 00:06:24,500
I've never met such a body refiner before!

92
00:06:24,770 --> 00:06:25,570
Pervert...

93
00:06:26,020 --> 00:06:28,110
This woman must be a pervert!

94
00:06:28,810 --> 00:06:29,480
Let go of me!

95
00:06:34,250 --> 00:06:35,460
But...

96
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:37,470
More, more, more!

97
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:39,140
I haven't had enough!

98
00:06:39,590 --> 00:06:41,190
Would you cut it out already?

99
00:06:41,270 --> 00:06:43,820
So gentle. Put your heart into it!

100
00:06:43,850 --> 00:06:45,590
Is that all you've got?

101
00:06:48,659 --> 00:06:50,620
Seriously, what's wrong with you?

102
00:06:57,420 --> 00:06:58,750
You're no match for her.

103
00:06:58,940 --> 00:07:00,869
Leave your last words and meet your end,

104
00:07:00,870 --> 00:07:01,670
Wang Xiaoxiu.

105
00:07:24,190 --> 00:07:27,440
Fine. You asked for it.

106
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:34,070
Wow, that felt so good!

107
00:07:39,150 --> 00:07:40,830
Too gentle!

108
00:07:53,940 --> 00:07:56,940
Take this! Take this! Take this! Take this! Take this!

109
00:07:59,300 --> 00:08:00,610
Give me more!

110
00:08:05,290 --> 00:08:05,950
Kui.

111
00:08:13,920 --> 00:08:15,370
Too gentle.

112
00:08:24,380 --> 00:08:26,280
Is that all you've got?

113
00:08:38,299 --> 00:08:39,760
Kui, calm down!

114
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:41,570
Don't activate your power!

115
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:46,130
Stay out of it, Stone.

116
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:49,240
I told you he's a great tonic.

117
00:08:51,950 --> 00:08:53,410
I must become stronger.

118
00:08:54,510 --> 00:08:57,940
So Stone and I can finally go somewhere where we're free.

119
00:09:01,520 --> 00:09:02,200
Kui...

120
00:09:58,820 --> 00:09:59,820
She's both strong

121
00:09:59,830 --> 00:10:00,920
and speedy.

122
00:10:01,470 --> 00:10:03,000
It's as if she's possessed.

123
00:10:03,490 --> 00:10:04,890
If I don't wanna die here,

124
00:10:05,520 --> 00:10:07,380
I'd better get my head in the game!

125
00:10:14,310 --> 00:10:15,870
I'm no pushover either!

126
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:21,640
Huh? No way!

127
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:41,370
I'm in paradise!

128
00:10:42,020 --> 00:10:42,580
Wait...

129
00:10:48,060 --> 00:10:49,210
Kui! No!

130
00:11:04,650 --> 00:11:05,960
What did I just see?

131
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:07,760
That woman's a monster!

132
00:11:13,810 --> 00:11:16,119
Kui leveled-up just from a lick of his blood!

133
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,850
How could his energy be so pure?

134
00:11:18,980 --> 00:11:20,000
What's going on?

135
00:11:26,490 --> 00:11:27,690
She's reverted back!

136
00:11:29,660 --> 00:11:31,920
This monster alone is already a problem.

137
00:11:32,290 --> 00:11:34,020
If that old man joins in too...

138
00:11:36,570 --> 00:11:37,430
No matter what,

139
00:11:38,040 --> 00:11:40,140
this is a rare opportunity.

140
00:11:44,130 --> 00:11:44,690
Damn it!

141
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:54,190
I was blown away just by his palm?

142
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:55,200
How'd he do that?

143
00:11:57,690 --> 00:11:58,529
I never thought

144
00:11:58,530 --> 00:11:59,860
Kui would level up here.

145
00:12:00,450 --> 00:12:02,130
Time's running out for Kui.

146
00:12:03,580 --> 00:12:04,710
Let's make it quick.

147
00:12:07,260 --> 00:12:08,980
You're quite strong, mister.

148
00:12:09,490 --> 00:12:10,490
Be my next victim.

149
00:12:10,780 --> 00:12:11,580
Cut the crap.

150
00:12:14,330 --> 00:12:15,510
Master, dodge!

151
00:12:17,400 --> 00:12:18,820
Dang! That was close!

152
00:12:20,560 --> 00:12:21,370
I missed.

153
00:12:21,710 --> 00:12:22,670
This is bad.

154
00:12:38,310 --> 00:12:39,170
He's done?

155
00:12:44,630 --> 00:12:45,360
Young fella.

156
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:48,570
Aren't you here to rescue that lady upstairs?

157
00:12:50,490 --> 00:12:51,530
Go along then.

158
00:12:51,980 --> 00:12:52,910
I'll let you off.

159
00:12:54,530 --> 00:12:55,990
Are you admitting defeat?

160
00:12:56,650 --> 00:12:58,050
Won't your boss kill you?

161
00:12:58,330 --> 00:12:58,730
You...

162
00:12:59,820 --> 00:13:01,350
If you're really giving up,

163
00:13:01,770 --> 00:13:04,849
you'd better not launch a sneak attack when my guard's down.

164
00:13:04,850 --> 00:13:06,379
I'm from the Million Alliance.

165
00:13:06,380 --> 00:13:07,710
Millions never give up!

166
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,180
What a nuisance.

167
00:13:09,430 --> 00:13:11,760
I'd never call a truce if she had more time.

168
00:13:12,410 --> 00:13:13,410
This benefits me.

169
00:13:13,910 --> 00:13:15,720
He's probably busy healing her.

170
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:19,539
But there's no guarantee they won't come at me once she's better.

171
00:13:19,540 --> 00:13:20,450
That'll be bad.

172
00:13:21,340 --> 00:13:23,050
Since you won't give up,

173
00:13:23,810 --> 00:13:25,610
that means our fight's not over.

174
00:13:25,900 --> 00:13:28,080
Are kids these days all so paranoid?

175
00:13:29,760 --> 00:13:32,260
Fine. I'll never admit defeat.

176
00:13:32,940 --> 00:13:34,159
But I can make a blood oath

177
00:13:34,160 --> 00:13:35,420
to quell your worries.

178
00:13:35,670 --> 00:13:37,470
This is the token of my Alliance,

179
00:13:37,550 --> 00:13:38,620
the Million Coin.

180
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:42,840
The blood oath is the greatest promise a cultivator can make.

181
00:13:47,910 --> 00:13:49,769
I, Million Stone of the Alliance,

182
00:13:49,770 --> 00:13:50,830
swear with my blood

183
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:52,530
that this truce is sincere.

184
00:13:52,650 --> 00:13:53,489
If I break the oath,

185
00:13:53,490 --> 00:13:54,490
I'll turn to dust!

186
00:13:58,930 --> 00:14:00,470
What... What are you doing?

187
00:14:02,770 --> 00:14:04,690
Nothing. For memory's sake.

188
00:14:05,290 --> 00:14:06,840
Breathe. Stay calm.

189
00:14:07,660 --> 00:14:08,920
Take it and go!

190
00:14:10,750 --> 00:14:12,100
This isn't fake, is it?

191
00:14:12,650 --> 00:14:13,910
Can I pawn it for money?

192
00:14:14,090 --> 00:14:16,090
Give it back if you don't believe me!

193
00:14:16,750 --> 00:14:19,210
Of course I trust a man of integrity like you.

194
00:14:19,430 --> 00:14:21,210
Nothing but trust here, my man.

195
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:23,790
I hope you'll mend your ways

196
00:14:23,810 --> 00:14:25,140
and behave yourselves.

197
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:26,400
I'm off to save a life.

198
00:14:29,060 --> 00:14:30,870
This is a critical moment.

199
00:14:31,390 --> 00:14:33,020
I must keep my cool.

200
00:14:33,730 --> 00:14:35,130
Be still like a mountain.

201
00:14:37,740 --> 00:14:38,970
Ye-Yes.

202
00:14:40,940 --> 00:14:42,450
So long, Mr. Stone.

203
00:14:48,770 --> 00:14:50,700
Kids these days are so scary.

204
00:14:55,290 --> 00:14:56,860
Misha, are you there?

205
00:14:57,570 --> 00:14:59,830
Our training mission's been suspended.

206
00:15:02,620 --> 00:15:03,910
Going back so soon?

207
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,570
Kui had an accident.

208
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,810
We have no other choice.

209
00:15:10,330 --> 00:15:11,409
What happened to her?

210
00:15:11,410 --> 00:15:12,859
It's inconvenient right now.

211
00:15:12,860 --> 00:15:14,060
Let's talk in person.

212
00:15:15,850 --> 00:15:16,350
Misha!

213
00:15:16,770 --> 00:15:17,570
Are you there?

214
00:15:18,330 --> 00:15:18,810
Misha.

215
00:15:19,180 --> 00:15:19,620
Misha!

216
00:15:20,370 --> 00:15:20,810
Misha!

217
00:15:25,650 --> 00:15:26,310
Who are you?

218
00:15:34,690 --> 00:15:35,550
Mr. Chu Mushan!

219
00:15:35,950 --> 00:15:37,080
Where are you going?

220
00:15:38,200 --> 00:15:39,860
Young Master, don't you know?

221
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:43,200
All your assassins have been wiped out.

222
00:15:44,190 --> 00:15:44,730
What?

223
00:15:45,890 --> 00:15:47,530
Uncle, is this true?

224
00:15:49,250 --> 00:15:51,280
Young Master. Change of plans.

225
00:15:51,870 --> 00:15:53,470
You must evacuate right now.

226
00:15:55,770 --> 00:15:57,180
What the hell's going on?

227
00:15:57,570 --> 00:15:58,710
It must be Xigu Qin!

228
00:16:00,190 --> 00:16:01,930
Forget Xigu Qin.

229
00:16:02,590 --> 00:16:05,340
I've found an even more interesting target.

230
00:16:13,670 --> 00:16:15,410
What... What on earth...

231
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:16,480
Young Master.

232
00:16:17,110 --> 00:16:20,159
The Million Alliance called a truce with the intruder.

233
00:16:20,160 --> 00:16:21,480
What?

234
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:22,950
Unfortunately,

235
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:24,990
your plan must be terminated.

236
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:26,530
What matters now is—

237
00:16:30,940 --> 00:16:32,030
I'm not leaving!

238
00:16:34,610 --> 00:16:35,480
Mr. Chu Mushan,

239
00:16:36,000 --> 00:16:37,660
you can help me finish my plan.

240
00:16:37,880 --> 00:16:38,679
I'll pay you double.

241
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:39,060
No!

242
00:16:39,200 --> 00:16:40,090
Triple the pay!

243
00:16:40,250 --> 00:16:40,720
Deal?

244
00:16:41,300 --> 00:16:42,000
Bastard!

245
00:16:42,140 --> 00:16:43,070
Watch out!

246
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:44,249
What...

247
00:16:44,250 --> 00:16:45,710
I've warned you many times

248
00:16:46,000 --> 00:16:48,110
not to use money to order me around!

249
00:16:48,690 --> 00:16:50,200
He's an erratic oddball.

250
00:16:50,460 --> 00:16:52,390
We can't afford to provoke him now.

251
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:56,040
The youngest and proudest of the Ominous Menaces,

252
00:16:56,280 --> 00:16:57,550
Chu Mushan.

253
00:17:05,089 --> 00:17:09,040
{\an8}[Next Episode Preview]

254
00:17:05,369 --> 00:17:07,450
It's an honor to meet you.

255
00:17:07,940 --> 00:17:11,140
We're called Chu Mushan.

256
00:17:12,550 --> 00:17:14,640
Cube, sure you're not mistaken?

257
00:17:14,670 --> 00:17:16,250
His combat power is just 7?

258
00:17:16,280 --> 00:17:19,280
Actually, aren't we born to be archenemies?

259
00:17:19,369 --> 00:17:23,119
I'm gonna stay here and watch all of you get blown up into mush!

260
00:17:23,520 --> 00:17:24,930
I was the cause of this.

261
00:17:25,869 --> 00:17:27,280
I'll take care of it.

262
00:17:27,569 --> 00:17:28,369
Uncle.

263
00:17:29,030 --> 00:17:30,320
Don't forget

264
00:17:31,210 --> 00:17:33,860
I still have a trump card to turn the tables.

265
00:17:34,280 --> 00:17:38,910
Anyone who sees this... must die!

266
00:17:53,070 --> 00:17:57,140
♪ Could it be that gravity also tilts toward you?♪

267
00:17:57,410 --> 00:18:01,610
♪ You start to shine brightly in the crowd ♪

268
00:18:01,630 --> 00:18:07,510
♪ Why do I suddenly feel this way?♪

269
00:18:10,170 --> 00:18:14,300
♪ Why is it that whenever I need you most ♪

270
00:18:14,330 --> 00:18:17,090
♪ You always appear?♪

271
00:18:17,410 --> 00:18:25,850
♪ Can you sense all of my emotions?♪

272
00:18:27,490 --> 00:18:31,330
♪ Sharing every little thing, all day long ♪

273
00:18:31,610 --> 00:18:35,450
♪ You've listened to all the songs I like ♪

274
00:18:35,600 --> 00:18:39,400
♪ The story has reached this point, just one step away ♪

275
00:18:39,660 --> 00:18:41,740
♪ Confessing ♪

276
00:18:43,370 --> 00:18:48,170
♪ Can you say the words you've been meaning to say to me?♪

277
00:18:48,190 --> 00:18:51,470
♪ Let impulse bloom like cherry blossoms ♪

278
00:18:51,500 --> 00:18:52,800
♪ My heart is fluttering ♪

279
00:18:52,830 --> 00:18:56,710
♪ A little bit of confusion, sweet but helpless ♪

280
00:18:56,820 --> 00:19:01,090
♪ A single gaze, and a happy surprise ♪

281
00:19:01,120 --> 00:19:05,150
♪ Can you tell me the answer I'm looking forward to?♪

282
00:19:05,410 --> 00:19:08,609
